modules.description: This module implements efficient, type-safe memory copying between different memory block types, including OCaml bytes, Bigarrays, Ctypes pointers, and C arrays. It provides direct copying operations with support for offsets and length specifications, enabling precise memory transfers between compatible structures. Concrete use cases include transferring data between OCaml-managed memory and C-allocated buffers, populating Bigarrays from byte strings, and directly manipulating memory-mapped regions.
